snippet.title: Speed Expansion Pack Trailer
snippet.description:
Download this trailer to check out the awesome Speed Expansion Pack for MotorStorm® Pacific Rift.

Now you can rip it up in paradise like never before with a host of extras. Take on three additional tracks and three track variants from the MotorStorm® Pacific Rift game with four previously unseen vehicles  each one kitted out with three unique paintjobs. Put your foot down in the Speed Weekend mini-festival, packed with 48 intense events plus unlockable rewards and trophies.

Purchase or use of this item is subject to the PlayStation®Network Terms of Service and this item's use restrictions.  If you do not wish to accept all these terms, do not purchase or use this item.  One time fee for downloads on up to five activated systems.

Video Output in HD requires cables and an HD compatible display, both sold separately.  This video will play on displays ranging from standard definition to 1080p.  However, this video will output at a maximum resolution of 720p.
